name: Rabbit Delirium #1
description:
Rabbit Delirium is my second collectible series, exclusive for Schizoid Bunny collectors.
If you have the whole series you will receive a special gift. If you have purchased 15 or more bunny editions, you will receive this Rabbit Delirium.
If you are an anonymous collector and agree to have me send it to you, please contact me somehow so I know.
